PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of WENDY LEE KELLY, of Regina, Saskatchewan, as a director of the Board of Directors of VIA Rail Canada Inc. to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, in the place of Francine Chad-Smith, whose term has expired.
